c: 40
v: 8
t: "Aey hamare Rubb, aur daakhil kar unko hamesha rehne wali un jannaton mein jinka tu ne unsey waada kiya hai, aur unke waldain aur biwiyon aur aulad mein se jo saleh (righteous) hon (unko bhi wahan unke saath pahuncha de). Tu bila shubah qadir e multaq (Most Mighty) aur hakeem(most wise) hai"